{"tid":1690974,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全體連登手足 支持＆感謝太古街坊","createTime":"2019-11-03T13:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T14:33:23.000Z","uid":90601,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"36cc91c236eeb79ffd05ac384e873c611df295ca","tid":1690974,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:01:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/on9ccnews/videos/451278445549655/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fon9ccnews%2Fvideos%2F451278445549655%2F&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQUzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=842311de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/on9ccnews/videos/451278445549655/</a><br />\n<br />\n睇片見到一出事 成班街坊己經赤手空拳湧上去救趙家賢<br />\n見到手足已經出盡力想拉開條仆街 四五個人狂打條友 條友頂唔順只能死拉住趙家賢<br />\n條仆街最後係俾人打到爆缸入廠 要記得條藍屍手上本身係有刀 街坊手足們可以即刻衝上去已經好犀利  唔好再話手足唔做野<br />\n<br />\n手足的確仲有好改善空間 可能需要訓練<br />\n例如千祈千祈唔好打斷人地手手腳腳 唔好踢人春袋 唔好劃花人地塊面<br />\n<br />\n唔該所有人<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>一齊感謝今日有出黎既太古手足</strong></span><br />\n香港人繼續反抗 還拖<br />\n分化撚 阻膠 全部同我返入你老母個閪度<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"a33f22aea07267f7f44ab1d0e2f045494e8d4a73","tid":1690974,"uid":68772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:02:11.000Z","msg":"手足你地好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57def348b9fbebfd2c87e812f519738a373cbea","tid":1690974,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c18641ba2864eb2c01d27587a8a2a095b8fe30","tid":1690974,"uid":155012,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:03:25.000Z","msg":"又打飛機，好撚嘔心<br />\n又係見好就收"},{"pid":"3baf757f39b17422196f42891d61adcddcd10510","tid":1690974,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b13c710a142